    <section_number>179</section_number>
    <catch_line>Placards Posted To Inform Employees</catch_line>
    <order_by>179</order_by>
    <text>
        The department may require employers to post in conspicuous positions in any place of employment such placards, posters or signs for the information of employees as it may issue.
    </text>
